graph LR
    MROperator[Model Registry Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    MROperator -->|metadata storage| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 16<br/>RHEL9]
    MROperator -->|alternative storage| MySQL[MySQL 8.x]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    MROperator -.->|auto TLS certs| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA]
    MROperator -.->|cert management| CertManager[cert-manager]
    MROperator -.->|service mesh| Istio[Istio Service Mesh 1.20+]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    MROperator -->|platform integration| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator]
    MROperator -.->|external ingress| IstioGateway[Istio Ingress Gateway]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH/RHOAI Dashboard] -.->|UI management| MROperator
    KServe[KServe] -.->|model metadata| MROperator
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|model tracking| MROperator

    %% Core Dependencies
    MROperator -->|CR reconciliation| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    MROperator -->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    MROperator -->|external routing| OSRouter[OpenShift Router]

    %% ConfigMaps
    ODHOperator -->|provides config| ServiceMeshRefs[ConfigMap:<br/>service-mesh-refs]
    ServiceMeshRefs -.->|Istio config| MROperator

    %% Database Selection
    PostgreSQL -.->|OR| MySQL

    %% Styling
    style MROperator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px

    %% External Required
    style PostgreSQL fill:#d79b00,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MySQL fill:#d79b00,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% External Optional
    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI
    style ODHOperator fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style IstioGateway fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style ServiceMeshRefs fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333

    %% Core Infrastructure
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style OSRouter fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
